data.description: This hard to find, four bedroom brick ranch on the South End boasts updated kitchen, flooring and bathroom. The Large 4th bedroom could be used as master, family room, play room or office. The oversized backyard has a big concrete patio with a large storage shed. This home is close to local amenities such as a gym, library, schools, multiple restaurants and parks. Paved driveway and new electrical panel done in 2020. Full enclosed privacy fence was also installed in 2022. Schedule for your showing today!
